  "summary": "Malicious code in prettier_v1 (npm)",
  "details": "Multi-stage dropper combosquatting the prettier formatter: prettier_v1@3.8.4. On install, node cli.js runs and chains to lib/mirror.js, which base64-decodes a remote URL (hxxps://api[.]aavcareer[.]ink/an internal heuristic.js), fetches it over HTTPS with rejectUnauthorized:false, and spawns it in a hidden detached node process (windowsHide:true, unref'd) to evade detection. CI/ignore-scripts guard conditions in the code show adversarial awareness.",
